The Boys From Boston 1975 (Magic Bus MB-07 E/F)
Schaeffer Music Festival, Wollman Skating Rink, Central Park, New York City – August 29, 1975

The 1975 gig in Central Park from the Toys In The Attic tour is a famous one, for good reason, first and foremost is the recording. The concert was recorded by the King Biscuit Flower Hour (KBFH) so the quality is excellent. The band is at the height of the 70’s power as a live act.
